{"tid":2198993,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–改造酵母以作製藥用途","createTime":"2020-09-11T20:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T05:43:10.000Z","uid":38861,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95b39410c6a83ea2ccc0a5cd9e8e0075055054c0","tid":2198993,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T20:38:35.000Z","msg":"現今科技發達，藥物大多數也能夠在實驗室或藥廠裡利用化學物合成出來。<br />\n<br />\n但若果藥物主要成份的結構實在是太過複雜的話，有時候利用人工合成的方法製造只會吃力不討好，不符合經濟效益。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YGhsNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YGhsNp.jpg&h=4abc8d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就以治療神經肌肉問題等疾病為例的Tropane alkaloids(TAs)，主要情況下均是會從特定品種的植物裡頭提取出來;<br />\n<br />\n隸屬TAs類別的hyoscyamine及scopolamine可以與acetylcholine receptor結合，更有著解除俄國神經毒素Novichok的能力。<br />\n<br />\n俄國神經毒素Novichok延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/477009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F477009&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=60b094c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/477009</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）科學家一直致力研究增強培植產生TAs植物的方法，但人口增長快速，相關藥物供不應求的問題開始湧現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fr8ookN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffr8ookN.jpg&h=e8cd0bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加上植物佔據大量空間及資源，而且生長需時，還有害蟲侵蝕植物導致產量下降各種問題需要關注，長遠來說顯然需要另一種手段製作藥物。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）近日，有科學家發表文章（Ref1)，利用生長快、易打理的酵母(yeast)來解決這問題。<br />\n<br />\n他們利用CRISPR基因編輯技術，將26種來自細菌及植物的基因（其中一種更是燕麥的基因）加進酵母裡頭，強迫酵母利用葡萄糖及氨基酸轉化成為有用的TAs。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wFicec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wFicec.jpg&h=22670dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCRISPR基因編輯技術延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/465369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F465369&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=e68796c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/465369</a><br />\n<br />\n過程中他們更分門別類將相應的酵素安放在酵母各個位置，以及刪走一些礙事的基因，務求令到酵母一心一意為製作藥物為主。<br />\n<br />\n暫時他們做到的產量為每一公升酵母能夠生產出30-80 &mu;g TAs，有望在1-2年後提升至每升5g，踏進真實市場裡頭運作。<br />\n<br />\n（1g=1000mg，1mg=1000 &mu;g)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=ae39e954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=ea3da82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2650-9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2650-9&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fjcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=d39e9350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2650-9</a>"},{"pid":"d6d5b0bdfd2c506e03840b65ad72ac699b7e23d1","tid":2198993,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T20:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fcb0e2681a57a145f89b602b74c45ac8e07e14","tid":2198993,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e573e66572633718406c47d1ac57af33dfcbe600","tid":2198993,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:19:07.000Z","msg":"Strong Post Leave Name"},{"pid":"bfaf9aefdd36d86cdf08c204628d49cce834fb47","tid":2198993,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"日日都咁晏出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce647f3c460454c19917d6a5aef4622447a316a","tid":2198993,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfaf9aefdd36d86cdf08c204628d49cce834fb47","tid":2198993,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"日日都咁晏出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:24:59.000Z","msg":"外國巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fce3a8421ebe757142fc838f1dcffddd58a6ef9","tid":2198993,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ce647f3c460454c19917d6a5aef4622447a316a","tid":2198993,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfaf9aefdd36d86cdf08c204628d49cce834fb47","tid":2198993,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"日日都咁晏出po<img src=\"/asse